вЂ‹Autoscaler: >    - A "Live Scaling" graph (simple CSS bars) showing Pod count over time.
вЂ‹Range sliders for Min/Max instances.
вЂ‹Diagnostics: >    - A black "Terminal" window.
вЂ‹"Run Check" button that types out lines of text: > Validating SSL... [OK], > Testing DB... [OK], > Checking Latency... 24ms.
вЂ‹Monitors: >    - Simple uptime cards (HTTP, Ping, SSL) with "99.99%" uptime percentages.
вЂ‹3. UI Branding:
вЂ‹Ensure all technical references (IDs, Names) are Orange Links.
